lenders.loan_because:
I'm a firm believer in solidarity rather than charity.  Kiva facilitates microloans that truly help people to help themselves, not "charity" or "handouts" that manage to keep them in poverty... plus, I have never not been paid back for a loan, so I just loan the same money over and over again.
